summary: A rock and mountain retexture in 2048x2048. Three version avalible: light gray, darker gray and colored.
descriptionHtml:
This is a rock and mountain retexture in 2048x2048. 

There are three version avalible: light gray, darker gray and colored. See images for comparison shots.

Install with Nexus Mod Manager or manually unzip and put the texture you want in the \"data\" folder.

Not much else to say. Did this one for myself and thought I\'d share it. 

Enjoy.
author: Majk360
